# Read-Before-Write Rule

Before modifying any file:

1. Identify boundaries — interfaces, types, schemas
2. Read upstream via @filename
3. State signatures in plan
4. Then edit

## Critique Checklist

- Null/empty values
- Network timeouts
- Race conditions
- Unhandled exceptions
